<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bn">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your Identity | MNA ServiceHub</title>
    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap");

      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f7fa;
        font-family:
          "Inter",
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI",
          Roboto,
          sans-serif;
        color: #1a202c;
      }

      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 40px 0;
        background-color: #f4f7fa;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0052cc 0%, #003d99 100%);
        padding: 40px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 35px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .content h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        color: #111827;
      }

      .content p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4b5563;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }

      .user-greeting {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #0052cc;
      }

      .otp-card {
        background-color: #f8faff;
        border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .otp-code {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #0052cc;
        letter-spacing: 12px;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .timer {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        background-color: #fff5f5;
        color: #c53030;
        padding: 6px 12px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
      }

      .footer p {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #94a3b8;
        margin: 4px 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .social-links {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .social-links a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #64748b;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0 10px;
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          width: 90%;
          margin: 20px auto;
        }
        .otp-code {
          font-size: 38px;
          letter-spacing: 8px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
          <h1>MNA ServiceHub</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
          <h2>Security Verification</h2>
          <p>
            Hello, <span class="user-greeting"><%= name %></span>!<br />
            To continue with your request, please use the following One-Time
            Password (OTP) to verify your identity.
          </p>

          <div class="otp-card">
            <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
            <div class="timer">⏱️ This code is valid for 3 minutes</div>
          </div>

          <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8">
            If you did not request this code, please ignore this email or
            contact our support team if you have concerns.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>
            &copy; 2026 <strong>MNA ServiceHub</strong>. All rights reserved.
          </p>
          <p>Chittagong, Bangladesh</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px">
            This is a system-generated email. Please do not reply to this
            address.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
